Is SunglassesDoge even remotely related to the "Godfather of DOGE" Musk?Abstract: Some time ago, the "godfather of dog coins" Musk called the wind and rain led to a cryptocurrency circle of animal frenzy, just shortly after this farce, a project called sunglasses dog quietly came out. The author's observation of the sunglasses dog shows that this project is inextricably linked to Musk.With DOGE before it and SunglassesDoge after it, Musk always seems to have something to do with dogcoin-related concepts.
